      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>1058</offset>
        <text>At several offshore sites, MGII abundance was highest in particle fractions, indicating that particle-attached MGII can outnumber free-living MGII under oligotrophic conditions.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">8</infon>
        <offset>1236</offset>
        <text>Compared with free-living MGII, the genome content of MGII in particle-associated fractions exhibits an increased capacity for surface adhesion, transcriptional regulation and catabolism of high molecular weight substrates.
</text>
        <annotation id="T5">
          <infon key="brat-id">T5</infon>
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <location length="29" offset="1350"/>
