      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">9</infon>
        <offset>1460</offset>
        <text>Moreover, MGII populations in POM fractions are phylogenetically distinct from and more diverse than free-living MGII.
</text>
        <annotation id="T11">
          <infon key="brat-id">T11</infon>
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
          <location length="24" offset="1579"/>
          <text>Eukaryotic phytoplankton</text>
        </annotation>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">10</infon>
        <offset>1579</offset>
        <text>Eukaryotic phytoplankton additions stimulated MGII growth in bottle incubations, providing the first MGII net growth rate measurements.
</text>
        <annotation id="T9">
          <infon key="brat-id">T9</infon>
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
